name: eHealthcare
description: Web Solutions for doctors and patients
overview:
eHealthcare provides web and IT solutions to doctors, dentists and patients in Japan.

ehealthcare provides web home pages to over 15,000 doctors and dentists as well as customer and employee satisfaction research, a free magazine that reaches two of the largest districts in Tokyo. eHealthcare operates the largest clinic/hospital web and mobile portal http://byoinnavi.jp/ in Japan, with over 2 million unique visitors each month and provides the only real-time, on-line, patient reservation service in Japan through this portal. This service is like ZocDoc in the US except japan has universal health care which make convenience a greater marketing point. It also operates Kanshinhiroba, which supports over 150 patient group non-profits.
